snippet.title: Find The Truth | Southeast Asia Games Onward 2024 Cut Trailer
snippet.description:
Find The Truth is a horror RPG puzzle game that revolves around a girl who has lost her memory due to an accident, and her journey to reclaim her lost memories. Your actions in the game will impact the story and lead to different outcomes.
